# textdomain: mcl_bone_meal

Bone meal is a white dye and also useful as a fertilizer to speed up the growth of many plants.=Kostna moka je belo barvilo in je uporabna tudi kot gnojilo za pospeševanje rasti številnih rastlin.

Rightclick a sheep to turn its wool white. Rightclick a plant to speed up its growth. Note that not all plants can be fertilized like this. When you rightclick a grass block, tall grass and flowers will grow all over the place.=Desno kliknite na ovco, da njeno volno obarvate belo. Desno kliknite na rastlino, da pospešite njeno rast. Upoštevajte, da vseh rastlin ni mogoče gnojiti na ta način. Ko desno kliknete na blok trave, bodo naokoli zrasle visoka trava in cvetlice.

Bone Meal=Kostna moka
Speeds up plant growth=Pospeši rast rastlin